==English==

===Adjective===
'''laxative'''
# having the effect of moving the [[bowel]]s, or aiding [[digestion]] and preventing [[constipation]].

====Translations====
{{top}}
*Dutch: [[laxerend]], [[laxerende]]
{{mid}}
*Spanish: [[laxante]]
{{bottom}}

===Noun===
'''laxative'''
# any substance, such as a food or in the form of a medicine which has a laxative effect.

